<%= content_for :title do %>
  Pagecord vs about.me: Personal landing page + blog. Free forever or $29/year.
<% end %>

<%= content_for :meta_description do %>
  about.me charges $72-90/year for a landing page with an AI chatbot. Pagecord gives you a landing page, blog, multiple pages, and custom domains for free or $29/year. No AI gimmicks, just solid features.
<% end %>

<div class="md:mt-4 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4">
  <h1 class="source-serif font-semibold text-center text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
    Pagecord: A Better about.me Alternative
  </h1>

  <div class="md:text-xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-y-4">
    <p class="mt-8 md:mt-12">
      about.me gives you a landing page with an AI chatbot for $72-90/year. That's it. One page that "talks back."
    </p>
    <p>
      Pagecord gives you a landing page too, but also a full blog, multiple pages (About, Now, Contact, Portfolio), themes, custom domains, and email-to-blog publishing. No AI chatbot, but you get way more for way less.
    </p>
    <p>
      Open source. Classic plan is free forever. Premium is $<%= localised_price %>/year.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-8 mb-4 md:text-xl">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-medium p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm btn-primary text-xl">Get your FREE account today</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

